@baseUrl = https://localhost:7115
@token = paste-access-token-here
@categoryId = 1

### Create Product
# Uses a seeded category id from a fresh database. Adjust if your database already had categories.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Manual Product",
  "description": "Created from REST client",
  "price": 99.99,
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}}
}

